# Policies

This section contains Ministry of Justice Digital, Data and Science policies and guidance.

## Current Policies

<% current_policies = sitemap.resources
	.select { |resource| resource.path.start_with?("policies/") && resource.path.end_with?(".html") && resource.data.policy_id }
	.sort_by do |resource|
		policy_id = resource.data.policy_id.to_s
		policy_number = policy_id[/\d+/].to_i
		[policy_number, policy_id, resource.data.title.to_s]
	end %>

<% if current_policies.any? %>
<% current_policies.each do |policy| %>
- [<%= policy.data.title %>](<%= policy.path.sub("policies/", "") %>) - <%= policy.data.policy_id %>
<% end %>
<% else %>
- No current policies published yet.
<% end %>

