## Using the Policy Template

Start at the [Choose a Policy Template](choose-a-template.html) page when creating a new policy. At the moment, the hub provides the [MoJ Policy Template](policy-template.html), and this page will grow as more approved templates are added.

For detailed step-by-step instructions, see [Adding a New Policy](adding-a-policy.html).
